data.description: Welcome to your new home! This charming 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom residence is situated approximately 6 miles from Moody Air Force Base, offering the perfect blend of convenience and tranquility. Nestled on a spacious .61-acre cul-de-sac lot, enjoy the luxury of space and privacy on a low-traffic road. Step inside to discover a cozy living area adorned with gorgeous LVP flooring, providing a timeless aesthetic that complements any decor.  The well-designed kitchen, conveniently connected to the living space, boasts a breakfast bar, ample cabinetry, and an attached dining area, creating a perfect setting for family meals and entertaining guests. The Owner's Suite serves as a private sanctuary after a long day, complete with its own bathroom.  Step outside to the privacy-fenced backyard, where a covered patio beckons for relaxation and outdoor gatherings. Benefit from the savings generated by the included solar panels, a modern eco-friendly feature that remains with the home. This property is eligible for 100% USDA financing, making your dream of homeownership more accessible than ever.  Don't miss the opportunity to make this wonderful house your home. Call today to schedule a tour and experience the warmth and comfort this residence has to offer!
